{"tid":2343621,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［真黃店推介］我永遠記得呢位真黃手足 賣紅酒嘅 各位幫襯吓","createTime":"2020-12-28T05:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T10:42:32.000Z","uid":187232,"like":67,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1c5dd16cfaf582c6e02c05c130351ce322cea4","tid":2343621,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"Sor呃咗你入嚟<br />\n因為見到批鬥黃店post好嬲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係黃店就ok 啦<br />\n講真香港地要零中國貨係好難<br />\n少賣中國貨係bonus <br />\n<br />\n就算係藍店賣外國貨，黃店賣中國貨都好，我地都唔會幫襯藍店架啦<br />\n係關立場問題，唔係貨品來源問題嘛⋯<br />\n點解要奄尖到黃店收皮先ok呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住比人屌「你依d一定係下次先投6號個班撚樣黎」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><em>挑你老味個臭high吖</em></strong></span><br />\n咁你批鬥哂掃低晒啲黃店囉<br />\n做生意易吖你估，衰咗就廿萬百萬咁蝕，真係想死架<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">我永遠記得有位真黃手足，賣紅酒嘅</span></span><br />\n喺抗爭初期，蝕到入肉喺又一城商場跳樓⋯⋯<br />\n事後報道問佢啲朋友，朋友們話「佢唔想用黃色名義賺錢，唔想比人有食人血感覺，生意點受影響都支持手足抗爭」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做生意嘅手足有蝕到幾辛酸有幾想死，但都堅持齊上齊落出錢出力<br />\n鬥黃L 個個大爺咁屌呢樣果樣，批鬥黃店當抗爭！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我屌哂你地老母吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />批鬥踩人就叻<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以唔好再批鬥黃店，當我求你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">最後希望大家唔好忘記死去嘅呢位<span class=\"xx-large\">賣紅酒的手足</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"9853a6102dd72d96380e02740941761593bb5a9c","tid":2343621,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"da031e5db0a14af588251fc466b3f341c359c352","tid":2343621,"uid":187232,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200318/IIPX6MF2JVNKDUWM3EGTTPXEPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200318%2FIIPX6MF2JVNKDUWM3EGTTPXEPA%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=a2212580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200318%2FIIPX6MF2JVNKDUWM3EGTTPXEPA%2F&h=18344939\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200318/IIPX6MF2JVNKDUWM3EGTTPXEPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n加埋啦<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa9e42c6cc375d37c102dd0a8220a13a375fc41","tid":2343621,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d82361a94d46d7b6b1c308f626e17a254630090d","tid":2343621,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:47:49.000Z","msg":"我都記得佢，推"},{"pid":"43efbd2769a8e6c9aa947ac3ac598abcdfaebd8e","tid":2343621,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e7e2ca6e589583b857794043e0dd26afd47900","tid":2343621,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:51:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ee3b38794094754bdfa3199bd0f80d43a5c5ce5","tid":2343621,"uid":17430,"like":0,"